<HEADLINE> Dolphins' Mixon Hurt in Accident </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	DAVIE, Fla. (AP) -- Miami Dolphins defensive end Kenny Mixon will  
miss Sunday's game at New England with abrasions and bruises 
suffered in a motorcycle accident. 
</P>
