<HEADLINE> Chamberlain Funeral To Be Saturday </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	LOS ANGELES (AP) -- A funeral for NBA Hall of Famer Wilt  
Chamberlain will be Saturday, his agent said. 
</P>
<P>
